                  </persName>
            . Q. Was there any specific mark by which you could swear to the loaves? A. No, they were outside loaves, and there was a bit out of the corner of one of them.</p>
               <p>COURT. Q. Did you miss them from where they had been? A. Yes; I heard the noise, and saw the back of the prisoner going out; I then followed, and took him.</p>
